{"tid":1164138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對華為禁令「有條件」延後90天實施 仍禁止採購生產新產品的零件和元件","createTime":"2019-05-21T01:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T01:50:37.000Z","uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9ba8ae3aadf85c4e38454adb3b471b0eae31c019","tid":1164138,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:01:09.000Z","msg":"川普政府20日宣布放寬16日對中國通訊設備大廠「華為」貿易黑名單的部分禁令90天，顯示此禁令可能對華為造成意料之外的深遠影響。<br />\n<br />\n商務部將允許華為購買美國商品，用以維持現有的網路，並對既有的華為裝置提供軟體更新。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過，華為仍被禁止購買美國零件，和用以製造新產品的組件</span>，這些組件需要執照許可但執照很可能遭駁回。<br />\n<br />\n上星期已經講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b902c6b4b9036c22e883946723b136d0e311db4f","tid":1164138,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e5f90072290ea10fb374e751123e8edd1f70bf","tid":1164138,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}